                  </persName>
            . The horse that my uncle ( the last witness) and I saw in Smithfield, is my father's property. He was in the custody of the prisoner when we found him.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence.</p>
               <p>I bought the horse, and gave seven guineas for him.</p>
               <p>To his Character.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17700117-42-person529">
