            . I am a labouring man, and live at Green-street-green. The prisoner lodged at my house nine months, or more. he went to day-labouring work. He always behaved very civil and honest.</p>
               <p>Q. Do you know of his being worth any quantity of money?</p>
               <p>Swainstand. I know nothing of that.</p>
